dcterms:description: This log records execution traces from a loan application process in a Dutch financial institution. The event log was split into two sub-logs, denoted with bpic2017 refused and bpic2017 cancelled.

dcterms:description: This event log originates from the Italian local police. The desired outcome is that a fine is fully paid, while in the undesired cases the fine needs to be sent for credit collection.
dcterms:title: Road traffic fines

dcterms:description: This event log corresponds to the Unemployment Beneﬁts scenario. The undesired outcome is that a resident will receive more beneﬁts than entitled, causing the need for a reclamation.
dcterms:title: Unemployment
